verbose_text: XREF_FIG D displays an example of a putatively genetically co-regulated gene-peak pair (r 2 between lead QTLs = 0.89), supporting the presence of a shared causal effect underlying the activity of an enhancer located in the second intron of SPIRE1 (H3K27ac-84963; chr18 : 12,551,731 -12,553,678) as well as SPIRE1 gene expression level.
